text: Michaela Jelínková (born 2 December 1985) is a Czech volleyball player. She played at the 2007 Women's European Volleyball Championship, 2009 Women's European Volleyball Championship, and 2010 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship. She played for USC Münster. == References == Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:Czech volleyball players
